org.apache.flink.cep.pattern

类 FollowedByPattern<T,F extends T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.cep.pattern.Pattern<T,F>
      • org.apache.flink.cep.pattern.FollowedByPattern<T,F>
  • 类型参数:
    T - Base type of the events
    F - Subtype of T to which the operator is currently constrained

    public class FollowedByPattern<T,F extends T>
extends Pattern<T,F>
    Pattern operator which signifies that the there is a non-strict temporal contiguity between itself and its preceding pattern operator. This means that there might be events in between two matching events. These events are then simply ignored.
